                <Header>President Woodrow Wilson</Header>
                <Paragraph>To learn about President Wilson's life and which of the Center's scholars are researching and writing about him, visit the "About Woodrow Wilson" web page.  The page also contains a bibliography, a list of other institutions that are dedicated to the former President, and some of his quotations.</Paragraph>
